# 🛍️ sustore

> **AI-Powered Digital Product Marketplace built on Shelby’s verifiable object storage**

sustore is a decentralized marketplace where creators can upload, sell, and distribute digital products — AI models, datasets, prompt packs, and media files — stored and served on [Shelby](https://developers.shelby.xyz), the world’s first verifiable global object storage for AI workloads.

-----

## 🚀 What sustore Does

- 🧠 **AI-powered discovery** — Smart recommendations using Shelby Skills & MCP agent tooling
- 🗄️ **Decentralized storage** — All files stored on Shelby’s S3-compatible hot storage (70% cheaper than AWS)
- 🔐 **Verifiable ownership** — Every purchase generates a cryptographic receipt anchored on Aptos
- 🖼️ **GenAI previews** — Product previews generated and distributed via Shelby Media Kit
- ⚡ **Global delivery** — Single global namespace, low-latency access from anywhere

-----

## 🏗️ Built With

- [Shelby Storage](https://developers.shelby.xyz) — S3-compatible verifiable object storage
- [Shelby MCP Server](https://developers.shelby.xyz) — AI agent tooling for smart product discovery
- [Shelby Media Kit](https://developers.shelby.xyz) — GenAI content distribution
- HTML / CSS / JavaScript — Frontend
- Node.js — Backend API

-----

