## 🛠️ Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js v18+
- A [Shelby](https://developers.shelby.xyz) developer account
- GitHub account

### Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/sustore.git
cd sustore
npm install
```

### Configuration

Create a `.env` file:

```env
SHELBY_API_KEY=your_shelby_api_key
SHELBY_BUCKET=sustore-products
PORT=3000
```

### Run Locally

```bash
npm start
```

Open your browser at `http://localhost:3000`

